OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FArmy lifts ban on serving  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsoldiers having beards     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Soldiers and officers are now allowed  
OL,6, to grow beards while serving in the    
OL,7, British Army.                          
OL,9,FThe beards and moustaches must be neat,
OL,10,Fproperly groomed and will be routinely 
OL,11,Fchecked.                               
OL,13,FThe policy comes into immediate effect 
OL,14,Fas the Army becomes the last of the    
OL,15,Farmed forces to allow its personnel to 
OL,16,Fgrow beards.                           
OL,18,FThe new directive follows years of     
OL,19,Fdiscussion around the Army's policy on 
OL,20,Ffacial hair.                           
